starrynite
----------

Required dependencies:

* libtiff

Optional dependencies:

* autoconf 2.6.1 or greater
* automake 1.10 or greater
* gperf

- autoconf is required to rebuild the configure script from configure.ac.
- automake can be used to regenerate the Makefile.in files used during the
  build.
- gperf is only required to regenerate the file parameters-tools.c from
  its source, parameters-tools.gperf.

To build this project, use:

configure [OPTION]... [VAR=VALUE]... && make && make install

For a list of configuration options:

configure --help
